c: 9
v: 117
t: "Nummah Yalli Nabii kee Muhaajiriniiy Ansaar deqsita maray gibdi wakti tabuuk gaaduh kaa kataatek keenik horták lubbitte cakkik makkoote raarra hayteek gamadal Yalli diggi ken heeh ken maqarroyseh, tohuk lakal Yalli toobat keenik oggoleh, diggah usuk moominiinih allaaqalli xuwaw-li kinni"